        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be an individual farmers/ farmers group/ Farmers Producer Organization (FPO)/ cooperative society or registered institution.\n   1. The applicant must have agricultural land a minimum of 0.25 acres and a maximum of 10 acres (25 acres for cluster area).\n   1. The applicant must be registered on the DBT portal.\n\n",
